e="preserve">Moin Nawaz Warraich (; born 22 February 1949) is a retired army officer and politician and the member of the Provincial Assembly of the Punjab since May 2013.
Early life and education.
Warraich was born on 22 February 1949 in Gujrat to Gul Nawaz Warraich. He completed his education from Pakistan Military Academy in 1970.
Military career.
Warraich is a Pakistan Army officer and has served as a Major until his retirement in 1995.
